        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "### 2c. Cleaning Data"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "# Hapus duplikat\n",
                "print(f'Shape sebelum hapus duplikat: {df.shape}')\n",
                "df = df.drop_duplicates()\n",
                "print(f'Shape setelah hapus duplikat: {df.shape}')\n",
                "\n",
                "# Reset index\n",
                "df = df.reset_index(drop=True)"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "# Handle missing values dengan forward fill (cocok untuk time-series)\n",
                "# Lakukan forward fill per stasiun untuk menjaga konsistensi\n",
                "print('Melakukan forward fill untuk missing values...')\n",
                "\n",
                "numeric_cols = ['PM2.5', 'PM10', 'SO2', 'NO2', 'CO', 'O3', 'TEMP', 'PRES', 'DEWP', 'RAIN', 'WSPM']\n",
                "\n",
                "# Forward fill per stasiun\n",
                "for col in numeric_cols:\n",
                "    df[col] = df.groupby('station')[col].transform(lambda x: x.ffill())\n",
                "\n",
                "# Jika masih ada missing values (di awal data), gunakan backward fill\n",
                "for col in numeric_cols:\n",
                "    df[col] = df.groupby('station')[col].transform(lambda x: x.bfill())\n",
                "\n",
                "print(f'Missing values setelah cleaning:')\n",
                "print(df[numeric_cols].isnull().sum())"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "# Buat kolom datetime dari year, month, day, hour\n",
                "df['datetime'] = pd.to_datetime(df[['year', 'month', 'day', 'hour']])\n",
                "\n",
                "# Hapus kolom year, month, day, hour yang sudah tidak diperlukan\n",
                "df = df.drop(columns=['year', 'month', 'day', 'hour'])\n",
                "\n",
                "# Pindahkan kolom datetime ke posisi pertama\n",
                "cols = df.columns.tolist()\n",
                "cols.insert(0, cols.pop(cols.index('datetime')))\n",
                "df = df[cols]\n",
                "\n",
                "print('Kolom datetime berhasil dibuat!')\n",
                "print(f'\\nRange datetime: {df[\"datetime\"].min()} sampai {df[\"datetime\"].max()}')"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "# Pastikan kolom numerik bertipe float\n",
                "numeric_cols = ['PM2.5', 'PM10', 'SO2', 'NO2', 'CO', 'O3', 'TEMP', 'PRES', 'DEWP', 'RAIN', 'WSPM']\n",
                "df[numeric_cols] = df[numeric_cols].astype(float)\n",
                "\n",
                "print('Tipe data setelah cleaning:')\n",
                "print(df.dtypes)"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "# Tampilkan shape DataFrame akhir\n",
                "print('=== DATA SETELAH CLEANING ===')\n",
                "print(f'Shape DataFrame: {df.shape}')\n",
                "print(f'\\nJumlah missing values: {df.isnull().sum().sum()}')\n",
                "print(f'Jumlah duplikat: {df.duplicated().sum()}')\n",
                "print(f'\\n5 baris pertama:')\n",
                "df.head()"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "> **Insight - Ringkasan Cleaning Data:**\n",
                "> \n",
                "> 1. **Duplikat dihapus:** {} baris duplikat berhasil dihapus.\n",
                "> \n",
                "> 2. **Missing values ditangani:** Menggunakan forward fill (ffill) dilanjutkan backward fill (bfill) per stasiun, cocok untuk data time-series.\n",
                "> \n",
                "> 3. **Kolom datetime dibuat:** Menggabungkan year, month, day, hour menjadi satu kolom datetime, lalu kolom-kolom tersebut dihapus.\n",
                "> \n",
                "> 4. **Tipe data disesuaikan:** Semua kolom numerik dikonversi ke float.\n",
                "> \n",
                "> 5. **Shape DataFrame akhir:** {} baris × {} kolom\n",
                "> \n",
                "> Data sekarang sudah bersih dan siap untuk analisis!".format(\n",">     df.duplicated().sum() + (420792 - df.shape[
                    0
                ]),  # Approximate\n",">     df.shape[
                    0
                ], df.shape[
                    1
                ]\n","> )"
            ]
        },
